items={[
  {
    title: 'Do I own the infrastructure?',
    description:
      "Yes, you own the infrastructure. We will help you set up the infrastructure, but you will have full control over it. We can also help you set up your own infrastructure if you prefer.",
  },
  {
    title: 'Can we use other tools besides Intercom?',
    description:
      "Yes! We're comforable working with a variety of tools. We can help you set up and manage a variety of tools, including Hubspot Chat, Drift, and more. If you have a specific tool you'd like to use, please let us know and we can help you set it up.",
  },
  {
    title: 'How many automations can I have?',
    description:
      'The number of automations managed by us is based on the plan you choose. From there, you can set up as many automations as you need that you manage. If you need us to handle more automations, you can upgrade your plan at any time.',
  },
  {
    title: 'What CRMs do you support',
    description:
      "We support a variety of CRMs, including Salesforce, Hubspot, and more. If you have a specific CRM you'd like to use, please let us know and we can help you set it up. We also offer a custom CRM solution that we can help you set up.",
  },
  {
    title: "What's your pricing?",
    description:
      "Our pricing is fully transparent and can be found on our pricing page. We offer a variety of plans to fit any budget, and we can also create a custom plan for you if you have specific needs. ",
  },
  {
    title: 'How do you handle credential sharing?',
    description:
      "We have a secure portal that you can use to share credentials with us and vice versa.",
  },
]}
/>

